                        Top Positive Review
                    


                        Excellent coverage of grey
                    

                            Posted by Reviewer2324933 on Jul 14, 2013
                    


                            This is not an easy to use product, but it really did a nice job of covering the grey in the front of my hair.  I had been using Surya and really loved the look and the ease of application, but it began to take on a pink tone, probably as my grey hair increased.  Naturally, it's all in the front.  This product did a nice job of covering it without making it look pink, but it is not that easy to apply.  I let the mixtures sit for 3 hours as one of the methods advised and the product was hard when it was time to apply.  I think adding a little water right before application might make application easier and still give good color.  I have re-ordered this product and am happy with the results, but it is not an easy product to apply.  It is in powder form and must be mixed to use.  
                        


                        3 people found this helpful
                    



