                        Top Critical Review
                    


                        very, very messy!!
                    

                            Posted by Reviewer2344866 on Sep 19, 2008
                    


                            I was so excited to try this all natural color/conditioner, but... it was horrible to work with!  I have to condition my hair much more now.  Had to wash my hair twice after coloring to get the grit and 'muddy' look out of it.  I'm very disappointed in this product.  You really do need a paintbrush to apply this; and you would definitely need two people!
                        


