What a great product.



                        Posted by 4703027820068945532 on Oct 11, 2016
                     | Verified Purchase


Color the grey. This product is amazing. I developed a nasty allergy to chemical hair dyes . This product hs saved my sanity. First of all it's easy and simple to order. Delivery is super fast. Instructions supplied are clearly written. Did a test patch as instructed then proceeded to apply. It mixes easy and coats hair beautifully.  Four hours later ...super shiny,glossy hair. The colour!. Wow!. It covered every single grey hair. It has reduced the frizz on my curly hair and it remains,four weeks later, so soft. Many thanks. Will not use another brand again!. X










