                    Email
                

























 Holistic Health
 


Remedies by Condition
 



	Natural Solutions for Gray Hair
		






 By Cathy Wong, ND  

| Reviewed by a board-certified physician





    	Updated April 30, 2017 
		












                    Share
                






                    Pin
                






                    Email
                







	    Print
	    











 

        Thomas Barwick/Iconica/Getty Images
    





