VInegar Rinse Cleanser Gray Hair Nutritive botanical Solutions

























 





 











 








 





















 




 













 


Gray HairVinegar Rinse Cleanser
 


 
 


When Shampoo Alone is Not Enough


 


Gray hair can turn yellow as residue that is left on your follicles from other products gives it a brassy and dull appearance.Products such as shampoo, conditioners, hair spray, mousse, and gels can leave a residue on the hair shaft that yellows. Avoiding such artificial products is crucial in maintaining your hair's look, but a cleanser is necessary when damage has already been done.An excellent way to restore, rejuvenate and add sparkle again to gray hair is with apple cider vinegar. Apple cider vinegar removes residue on your hair strands leftover from hair care products.Frizzy, coarse and unmanageable strands is a common concern that a vinegar rinse can also help solve by dually working as a detangler and anti-frizz product.When regularly used in your hair care routine, apple cider vinegar can revitalize your hair, leaving it soft and smooth.
 










 


 


 




 











 



















 
























 













 





 











 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 


 
 
Benefits
 
 



















 
 


 
 
 
 
 
 


 
 
Apple Cider Vinegar has been used for centuries to cleanse and detox dry hair.Dry hair will be able to receive nutrients from other products, leaving it moisturized, vibrant and healthier.This should be the first product to use when you have dry hair problems as it deep cleanses toxins away from follicles and encourages responsive hydrated hair.
 









 
 


 
 
 
 
 


Free of residue and toxins, your hair will feel and become healthier as it starts to breathe and rejuvenate itself.Restores manageability, luster and volume to dry, lifeless hair. Balances the pH and brightens hair color and shine.Choking residue is removed from around hair follicles, which can cause hair to be dull, weak, frizzy and subject to breakage.Color safe and color enhancing as nutrients nourish follicles for hair that is restored with more radiant color and shine.Made fresh in the USA.  Apple Cider Vinegar contains nutritive alpha hydroxy acids, loaded with vitamins and minerals and helps to regulate pH levels.Naturally anti-bacterial and anti-fungal, which helps provide friendly environment for healthy hair growth.Free of harsh detergents like Sodium Lauryl Sulfate or Sodium Laureth Sulfate. Gentle, safe, non-irritating, and all nutritive formula.Nature’s best ingredients provide nutrients with vitamins that feed and hydrate for the best looking fullest healthy hair growth.Herbal extracts from Nettle Root, Comfrey Root, Plantain, Horsetail, Guava, Banaba Leaf and Burdock Root detoxify and cleanse to revitalize dry hair.Panthenol Pro-Vitamin B5 strengthens hair while dirt, sebum and dead skin cells are lifted away from follicles.Avocado oil quickly penetrates hair strands to add lightweight moisture and manageability.Anti-fade, color safe formula keeps hair color longer. Chloride free, sulfate free and protects color from sun, wind and pool water damage. Color is sealed in to last longer.Keratin straightening treatments, perms, colors and other hair treatments are maintained and protected.Hair is left hydrated, vibrant, untangled, strengthened, and damage-free.


 




















 













 





 











 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 


 
 
How to Use
 
 









 
 


 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 


 
 
Shake well.After shampooing your hair, apply an adequate amount to your hair and scalp.Massage your scalp gently.
 
 
 
 


 
 
Next, massage from your roots to your hair tips.Leave the rinse on for one to three minutes, then rinse well with warm water.Follow with conditioner, and style as usual.Use every fifteen days or as needed to remove buildup and maintain your scalp's health.Excellent for keeping in new color. Color safe.
 


 
 
 
 
 
 


 




















 













 





 













 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 


 
 
